I‘m still so heartbroken over the news about Wendy’s injuries, especially when watching this video. She looks so happy, healthy and is just completely slaying her highnotes and now she doesn’t have the chance to promote because of something that could have easily been prevented. I hope that SBS will face consequences and that not only SBS but also other channels/hosts (or whatever you call it) learn that they have to keep the performers in a save environment without any dangerous spots like the SBS stage had or at least let them know about those spots and constantly remind the performers about them.
I hope Wendy can take her time to fully recover and when she’s ready to come back, she will completely own this era💜
